crs:Helmert.crs:Name: NZGD49 to WGS 84 (2)
crs:Helmert.crs:Description: hese parameter values are taken from NZGD49 to NZGD2000 (4) (code 1701) and assume that NZGD2000 and WGS 84 are coincident to within the accuracy of the transformation. For improved accuracy use NZGD49 to WGS 84 (4) (code 1670).

crs:Helmert.crs:Name: DHDN to WGS 84
crs:Helmert.crs:Description: Parameter values from DHDN to ETRS89 (2) (code 1776) assuming that ETRS89 is equivalent to WGS 84 within the accuracy of the transformation. Replaces DHDN to WGS 84 (1) (tfm code 1673).
